http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/%E2%80%98No-central-team-let-Mamata-govt-handle-Malda%E2%80%99/article13997419.ece

The Centre on Wednesday said will not send any official team to West Bengal, as demanded by the BJP, as of now to probe the violence in Malda, where protesters had set fire to a police station and damaged several vehicles, leading to tension in the area.“As of now, no central team will visit. Since law and order is a State subject, let the West Bengal government handle the situation,” a Home Ministry official said.A three-member BJP delegation had on Tuesday met Home Minister Rajnath Singh and demanded a high-level probe into the >Malda violence, alleging it had links with fake currency and narcotics trade and infiltration.